{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-js","path":"/franz-schmidt/","result":{"data":{"prismicProject":{"uid":"franz-schmidt","id":"a9a2649f-336e-58f0-9059-4ad1a280ed59","data":{"project_title":{"html":"<p>Weaving Fabric for Suits</p>","text":"Weaving Fabric for Suits"},"client":{"html":"<p>Franz Schmidt</p>","text":"Franz Schmidt"},"location":{"html":"<p>Oslo, NW</p>","text":"Oslo, NW"},"team":{"html":"<p>Theo Ford, Jonas Topooco, Daniel Olsson (Research &amp; Development)</p>","text":"Theo Ford, Jonas Topooco, Daniel Olsson (Research & Development)"},"year":{"html":"<p>2015</p>","text":"2015"},"categories":[{"category":{"slug":"print","id":"ZMfXERAAACIAPs4i"}}],"body1":[{"id":"text$adf075dc-b14e-4529-856b-960d3d5fd97e","slice_type":"text","primary":{"text":{"html":"<p>Whilst working at Research &amp; Development I worked on the design and photographic art direction for Franz Schmidt &#39;Weaving Fabrics for Suits&#39;, developed within the Norwegian Artistic Research Programme at the department of Art and Craft at the Oslo National Academy of the Arts. The catalogue is published as part of both the exhibition with the same title at Oslo Kunstforening March 13 — April 19, 2015. The book presents Schmidt&#39;s research study in mapping Norway&#39;s forgotten textile production from the past: the factories, the tools, the materials, the designs, the production methods, the economy, the history, the people. </p>","text":"Whilst working at Research & Development I worked on the design and photographic art direction for Franz Schmidt 'Weaving Fabrics for Suits', developed within the Norwegian Artistic Research Programme at the department of Art and Craft at the Oslo National Academy of the Arts. The catalogue is published as part of both the exhibition with the same title at Oslo Kunstforening March 13 — April 19, 2015. The book presents Schmidt's research study in mapping Norway's forgotten textile production from the past: the factories, the tools, t